<div class="section-description">
	                            <div class="attribute-short">
                    
<p>Hacker News Delta Security is a team effort. We recommend:</p><p>If you find a security hole, please let us know at <a href="mailto:security@se7enx.com" target="_self">security@se7enx.com</a>.</p><p>We try to respond (with fixes!) as soon as possible, and really appreciate the help.</p>                </div>
                    
                    <div class="attribute-long rich-text">
                
<p>Thanks to the following people who have discovered and responsibly disclosed security holes in Hacker News Delta:</p>
<ul>

<li>No Issues Reported to Date (*<b><sub><sup>2026/01/18</sup></sub></b>)</li>

</ul>
